{"tid":2347709,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【黎智英還押】法夢比卡超：馬道立李義張舉能，你哋up乜春呀？","createTime":"2020-12-31T08:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T14:21:34.000Z","uid":138409,"like":188,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"f883cd45119223e2ea753de90e880732108f1d92","tid":2347709,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:54:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/3601293943317197\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEdInDisguise%2Fposts%2F3601293943317197&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm6%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=5db92981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EdInDisguise/posts/3601293943317197</a><br />\n<br />\n馬李張嘅邏輯係<br />\n1. 總裁判官拒絕保釋<br />\n2. 原訟庭給予保釋<br />\n3. 終審法院上訴委員會就2給予上訴許可<br />\n<br />\n3代表2「可能（arguably）」法律上出錯，所以為了「維持/回復現狀」，要去返1<br />\n問題係，每一次原審法庭同上訴法庭得出不同結論，而上訴委員會其後就後者的決定給予上訴許可，都必然代表上訴法庭「可能（arguably）」法律上出錯，咁係咪每次「中級上訴法庭」做嘅保釋決定都自動無效？<br />\n<br />\n換言之，原審唔畀保釋而上訴選擇畀，只要CFA就上訴判決畀上訴許可律政司，為了「維持/回復現狀」，就必然無得保釋？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">但相反地，係咪原審畀保釋而上訴唔畀，而CFA就上訴判決畀上訴許可上訴人，為了「維持/回復現狀」，就反而必然有得保釋先？<br />\n<br />\n你哋up乜春呀馬李張？</span>"},{"pid":"b9737a925c75bc569e0b0ee9ccf1eb6de63567c0","tid":2347709,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"36923f7adc9d9c934df05f7944d9d0d8a4ded0a7","tid":2347709,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7478e6eb4b50ce04bd7e7e02ff0297f67f623e34","tid":2347709,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510d87925be585e867b0045b60fdddc87c37c2af","tid":2347709,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"